race.comment: MISS CHARMED (1) drew this same box last time when in the minors (19.56) in a Grade 5 over 350m at this track. Key player on best form. GRETA'S GOLD (5) is a sprinter who thrives over these shorter races. Kept coming to fill the minor placings over 350m at this track (19.54) in a Grade 5. Strike rate this course and distance strong having won three of five tries. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card last start despite being beaten. Hard to beat again. ALL IN OLLIE (7) had been in super honest form hitting the frame three times on end before finishing fourth (19.78) at this track last time. Form here at the trip sound including eight wins. Should be in this for a long way. DONEGAL EXPRESS (3) did a good job to finish second last time out over 350m at this track (19.65) in a Grade 5, the second top-three finish on the trot.
